source.name: FY11_TSGLI Claimants and Payments by Type of Loss
source.description: The Servicemembers' Group Life Insurance Traumatic Injury Protection Program (TSGLI) Claimants and Payments by Type of Loss dataset provides the number of claimants approved, the dollar amount paid, and the average payment for each type of loss.
